OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: John
OL,4,CGillespie
OL,6,FJohn Gillespie, Age 104, Royal
OL,7,FEngineers
OL,9,FInterviewed by ITN 6 June 2024
OL,11,FBrought up in Glasgow and trained in
OL,12,Fcivil engineering, Mr Gillespie went
OL,13,Fto Normandy to work on projects
OL,14,Fincluding Pluto - Pipelines Under The
OL,15,FOcean.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
