OL,4,CGillespie
OL,6,FHe had trained with the Royal
OL,7,FEngineers in Aldershot and the
OL,8,Fregiment was tasked with implementing
OL,9,Fthis impressive technical feat. PLUTO
OL,10,Fwas a scheme to supply the advancing
OL,11,Farmies with a ready supply of fuel
OL,12,Fonce they had landed in Northern
OL,13,FFrance.
OL,15,FThe Allies built an integrated network
OL,16,Fof pipes from oil terminals to pumping
OL,17,Fstations that were built and disguised
OL,18,Fon the Southern coast.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
