OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: John
OL,4,CGillespie
OL,6,FThe fuel then ran through submarine
OL,7,Foil pipelines put together under the
OL,8,FEnglish Channel. One set went from
OL,9,FDungeness to Calais and the other from
OL,10,Fthe Isle of Wight to Cherbourg.
OL,12,FMr Gillespie - who had made the
OL,13,Fcrossing from Portsmouth to Gold Beach
OL,14,F- was part of the team that built
OL,15,Fsteel petrol storage tanks on the
OL,16,FFrench coast to allow fuel to be
OL,17,Fcollected and distributed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
