OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: John
OL,4,CGillespie
OL,6,FThis included fuel that was pumped
OL,7,Fship-to-shore although oil tankers had
OL,8,Fbeen ruled out as the sole means of
OL,9,Ftransporting supplies. Partly because
OL,10,Fof the risk of air attacks while they
OL,11,Fwere moored offshore.
OL,13,FPLUTO was up and running by August of
OL,14,F1944 and by the end of the war had
OL,15,Fdelivered millions of tonnes of fuel.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
