OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: John
OL,4,CGillespie
OL,6,F"I was thinking about the wider
OL,7,Faspect," he said.
OL,9,F"The war affected me because my war
OL,10,Fstarted in 1939 as a civil engineer
OL,11,Fwith McAlpines and we were at
OL,12,FClydebank and we were building
OL,13,Fmunitions factories to make track
OL,14,Flinks for tanks in the Singer sewing
OL,15,Fmachine works.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
