OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: John
OL,4,CGillespie
OL,6,F"And every week two of the staff had
OL,7,Fto do the air raid warnings and so on
OL,8,Fthe Monday I was on duty in the office
OL,9,Fovernight with a Spanish engineer and
OL,10,Fthe next night was the Clydebank blitz
OL,11,Fand the two colleagues who were on
OL,12,Fduty in the office, they were killed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
