OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: John
OL,4,CGillespie
OL,6,F"I was on duty on the Monday and they
OL,7,Fdied on the Tuesday. My brother was in
OL,8,Fbomber command. He was killed. On the
OL,9,Flanding there were two companies in
OL,10,FPluto, the engineer company and the
OL,11,Flanding craft, and one of them was
OL,12,Fbombed, sunk and they were all killed.
OL,13,FAnd on the beachhead I transferred to
OL,14,Ftake his unit. I knew them all because
OL,15,Fboth of us had trained together.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
