OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: John
OL,4,CGillespie
OL,6,F"They say, why not me? For example, we
OL,7,Fended up Normandy to the Baltic and
OL,8,Fthen went on leave to go to Japan. And
OL,9,Fwhen I was on leave and we were
OL,10,Fmarried at the time, they dropped the
OL,11,Ftwo atomic bombs.
OL,13,F"I didn't go to Japan. I wouldn't have
OL,14,Fbeen here today if I had gone to
OL,15,FJapan. And so these are the memories I
OL,16,Fwas going through today."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/9
